---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import portrait from '../assets/martin-opedal.jpg';
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">Profile</span>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <Image
        src={portrait}
        alt="Portrait of Martin Opedal, Lead Cloud Solution Architect at Microsoft"
        widths={[200, 320, 400]}
        sizes="(min-width: 768px) 220px, 160px"
        class="about-photo"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          I've been working with Azure, Entra and M365 since 2011. I spent 15
          years running datacenter operations and cloud migrations side by side
          at Teknograd, Advania, Avanade and Sopra Steria before joining
          Microsoft. Most of my landing zone opinions trace back to something
          that failed in physical infrastructure or broke in an ExpressRoute
          config.
        </p>
        <p>
          Now I architect Azure Landing Zones, AKS Automatic, and AI Foundry
          deployments for Nordic enterprises. I use Terraform daily. The modules
          I ship come from real customer engagements, not theory.
        </p>
        <p>
          I co-founded two craft breweries. Fermentation and infrastructure both
          need the right controls and patience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
